Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.servlet.navigation.NodeContainer
      • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.servlet.navigation.Node
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExactNode, ExternalNode, ParentNode

    public abstract class Node
extends NodeContainer
implements java.io.Externalizable
    This represents a node in the navigational menu. Its a lightweight representation of the information built by the NavigationMenuService. It can be sub-classed to support different matching methods.
